0.98.name: wordpress/dirtysuds-embed-rss
0.98.description: Will add a list of links to items in a given feed. Simply include the URL for an RSS feed on it's own line, or wrapped in the embed tag like [embed]http://example.com/feed.rss[/embed] and the plugin will embed the feed the page with links to each item. The url must end with .rss
